events.name: Open Floor! Business Users and Developers Meet-up!
events.description: Time for another Meetup !! Hello everyone,  Our next meetup is scheduled on Sep 22 at Salesforce office and would be great to have you there. We will be speaking about some new exciting features for developers and together lets collaborate with Salesforce Customer Group to discuss on any business problems. You will also have the chance to network with the new prospects and existing customers. A new career opportunity or a new business opportunity or a new learning opportunity? You never know what this meet up is holding for you unless you drop by.  Agenda: 6:30 to 6:45 : Kick-Off and Introduction 6:45 to 7:30 : Lightning Ux, Components, App Builder and RoadMap - by Siva and Manish 7:30 to 8:00 : Celebrating 4 Milion App Exchanges - by Johan 8:00 - 8:15   : Solution to a Problem We have limited seats for registration as we are combining Customer and Developer groups, the seats are limited. Hurry up and RSVP now!
events.location: Salesforce Office, 9 Temasek Boulevard, #40-01, Suntec Tower 2 , Singapore
